#### Vision services
{% if VISION_RUN_CLICKHOUSE %}
---
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: vision-clickhouse
spec:
  type: NodePort
  ports:
    - port: 8123
      protocol: TCP
      name: "native"
    - port: 9000
      protocol: TCP
      name: "http"
  selector:
    app.kubernetes.io/name: vision-clickhouse
{% endif %}
